Package de.intarsys.security.smartcard.card.standard

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    StandardCard
    The abstraction of a smartcard inserted in a StandardCardTerminal.
    StandardCardConnection
    The abstraction of a connection opened to a StandardCard.
    StandardCardSystem
    The abstraction of the smartcard environment connected to the system.
    StandardCardTerminal
    The abstraction of a single terminal, optionally containing a token, connected to the system.
